parameters:
Thief Nora: Wow, it's amazing! Now I understand why Piste-
san wanted to come!
Receptionist Piste: Hehe, I'm glad you're happy.

Receptionist Piste: I was brought here by the great late
guild master, the widow.

Receptionist Piste: We talked about various things, like
the guild, cooking, work, and life.

Receptionist Piste: They taught me the importance and
significance of supporting someone, which I never thought I
could do anything about in the guild.

Priestess Sophia: She really was a wonderful person, wasn't
she?

Receptionist Piste: Agonia-san, Storge-san, Shimosu-san...
Everyone in the guild has been influenced by the great late
guild master.

Receptionist Piste: I believe that the idea of the guild
master being the symbol of the guild is undoubtedly the
legacy of the great late widow.

Mage Relm: We call you by a nickname, but what is your real
name?

Storge of Compassion: No one knows, I never revealed my
name until I died.

Storge of Compassion: When I asked, she said she had lost
her name. The only thing I know is that she was a
noblewoman.

Receptionist Piste: As for me, I don't really care about
names. I will always remember those hands, that voice, and
that gaze.

Receptionist Piste: No matter what happens, I will never
forget.

Receptionist Piste: I think that wanting to remember
someone is proof of a person who lived with all their
might.

Receptionist Piste: I really wanted Clea-chan, who will
carry the future of the guild, to come here no matter what.

Receptionist Piste: I'm not good at explaining things with
words, so I would be happy if Clea-chan could come here and
understand something.

Clea: Thank you very much. I also thought that I should
listen and know about it.

Receptionist Piste: We need to fulfill another objective!
Now, please help me collect the mint growing by the water!

Storge of Compassion: You noticed my tailing quite well.
Your alertness honed through practical combat is
impressive.

Storge of Compassion: The green mantle is the symbol of the
Adventurer's Guild. Clea has carried this symbol and run all
the way here.

Storge of Compassion: By some stroke of luck, I managed to
annihilate the Tomos Raiders, our archenemies, without being
crushed by the weight of the mantle.

Storge of Compassion: I alone cannot make the judgment,
but... I believe Clea has the qualifications to take the
final test.
Clea: Is this the final test?

Storge of Compassion: Please carefully examine the contents
of the request as an assignment from the guild and decide
whether to take on the challenge.

Clea (Is this the final test... about promotion within the
guild?)

Receptionist Piste: Alright, this should be enough! Now
that we have all the ingredients, let's head back to the
guild!

Thief Nora: What kind of dish can you make? Can I also have
some, Piste-san?

Receptionist Piste: I'll try making it with the recipe of
the Great Widow. Of course, I'll treat Clea-chan and the
others to it!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
実績 懐かしき場所
